      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get the muscle metaphor, but can you be a bit more technical? how does the bond between the steel and the concrete actually work to transfer those loads? like, why doesn't the steel just slip out of the concrete when it's under tension?",
      "source": "evaluator"
